text.tspan: Price changes in consumer goods and services in the USA, United States,
Price change in consumer goods and services in the USA, measured as the percentage change since 1997. Data is measured
based on the reported consumer price index (CPI) for national average urban consumer prices.
Source: United States Bureau of Labor Statistics (BLS)
